---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog & Engineering | ToolGrid" description="Technical deep dives into WebAssembly, browser architecture, and modern web development.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Blog & Engineering</h1>
      
      <div class="grid gap-8 mt-12">
        <article class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:bg-card transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-accent font-medium mb-2">Engineering • June 2026</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 hover:text-accent transition-colors cursor-pointer">The Death of Cloud Processing: Why Local WASM is the Future</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">SaaS companies have spent a decade convincing us that we need to upload everything to the cloud. We explore why WebAssembly is bringing the compute back to the client, slashing server costs to zero.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">Read Full Article →</a>
        </article>

        <article class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:bg-card transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-accent font-medium mb-2">Career • May 2026</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 hover:text-accent transition-colors cursor-pointer">How to Optimize Your Resume for ATS Scanners in 2026</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">A deep dive into how Applicant Tracking Systems actually parse your PDF resume, and why our free ATS Matcher tool uses localized TF-IDF algorithms to beat them.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">Read Full Article →</a>
        </article>

        <article class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card/50 hover:bg-card transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-accent font-medium mb-2">Privacy • April 2026</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 hover:text-accent transition-colors cursor-pointer">Why Zero-Trust Architecture Matters for B2B Data Cleaning</h2>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">When you upload a CRM export or a CSV lead list to a random online tool, you are violating GDPR and exposing your company to massive risk. Here is how local processing solves this.</p>
          <a href="#" class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent hover:underline">Read Full Article →</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
